haqeeqat is a 1964 hindi-language indian feature film directed by chetan anand and produced by chetan anand . the film stars balraj sahni , tabu , priya anand , sanjay khan , prem chopra , prem nazir , prem nazir , prem nazir , thikkurissi sukumaran nair and prem chopra . the film is based on the 1962 novel of the same name .